; margin-left: auto; font-family: Merriweather; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 2 !important;\">– Đối với Trang sức Bạc, Hợp kim cao cấp: Mỗi 500,000Đ chi tiêu, giảm 50.000Đ (áp dụng cho nhãn hàng PNJSilver, Disney|PNJ, PNJ Hello Kitty, Style by PNJ).</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 21px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Merriweather; font-size: 18px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"7\" class=\"wp-image-21058 entered td-animation-stack-type0-2 lazyloaded\" width=\"704\" height=\"704\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-300x300.png 300w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-150x150.png 150w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-768x768.png 768w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-696x696.png 696w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-1068x1068.png 1068w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-96x96.png 96w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7.png 1200w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\" title=\"CÙNG PNJ ĐÓN ƯU ĐÃI VÔ CỰC, HÒA SẮC CÙNG THẦN TƯỢNG 2\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-1024x1024.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\" srcset=\"https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-300x300.png 300w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-150x150.png 150w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-768x768.png 768w, https://www.pnj.com.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/7-696x696.png 696w, https://www.pn